description: Coconut macaroons are easy to whip up and delicious with a cup of coffee.
name: Coconut Macaroons Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Fold in the coconut and vanilla and leave to stand for 10 minutes. Scoop teaspoons of the mix into your hand and roll into balls. Place on a lined baking sheet and bake for 1012 minutes.
